comments: She goes on tangents and gets off topic a lot but the class is cool and she makes it interesting.

tag_professor: Caring (2)  Inspirational (1)  Get ready to read (1)  Respected (1)  Hilarious (1)  Gives good feedback (1)
comments: Angela was super helpful and would often go off topic to answer students questions or give tips for our terrible placements. She had many different teaching strategies. She would lecture, do group activities, bring candy. She even suggested the whole class wear pj\'s to class one night. She would teach until 9, but time would fly.

tag_professor: Caring (2)  Inspirational (1)  Get ready to read (1)  Respected (1)  Hilarious (1)  Gives good feedback (1)
comments: Angela is fantastic! She is alive and full of energy. There was never a dull moment in this course. I anxiously looked forward to every class. She gave CBT a new meaning.Our last class was held after all papers and tests were completed and although attendance was not required, over 2/3 of the students came which was a true tribute to Angela!

tag_professor: Caring (2)  Inspirational (1)  Get ready to read (1)  Respected (1)  Hilarious (1)  Gives good feedback (1)
comments: Angela is HILARIOUS! absolutely LOVE taking her class. She keeps everything very interesting, especially when she relates it to the real world. I look forward to this class every single week

tag_professor: Caring (2)  Inspirational (1)  Get ready to read (1)  Respected (1)  Hilarious (1)  Gives good feedback (1)
comments: Some may not like the casual and colloquial tone of this class and Prof but I loved it. Kept a night class entertaining, maintained attention. Only class so far where students have really gotten a good opportunity to process experiences in field/job. Although she acts kinda goofy she takes this work very seriously and that shows too. Recommend!

tag_professor: Caring (2)  Inspirational (1)  Get ready to read (1)  Respected (1)  Hilarious (1)  Gives good feedback (1)
comments: Angela does have a brash sense of humor but she won\'t hesitate to tone it down if it\'s offensive for you. She is very relaxed in class and keeps it as interesting as possible. Grades fairly and in a reasonable amount of time. I highly recommend her if you\'re not easily offended!

tag_professor: Caring (2)  Inspirational (1)  Get ready to read (1)  Respected (1)  Hilarious (1)  Gives good feedback (1)
comments: Crude, rough, rude. Unreasonable and inflexible. This professor needs to hone her social skills and learn some compassion. Who else docks someone points for absences related to the death of a close family member??? Can\'t recommend this professor.

comments: Good class, uses the book (an autobiography) as if it is an open case which is helpful for concept application. She uses humor and personal experience to drive points home. Fair but tough with grades. Has class favorites.
